Rating: 3
Very good. Like other reviewers, I served this over a small bed of angel hair pasta. I also doubled the chili garlic sauce and the fish sauce since we like Asian flavors here. The sauce is probably 8 times what is needed, so half or quarter the recipe and you'll still have plenty left over, which is great because it's quite tasty. I plan to use it on a pork tenderloin tomorrow night.

