Rating: 4
Excellent recipe especially the sauce which can be used on any fish or poultry maybe even pork. I made the full recipe for 2 of us as a main course and served it with a quinoa side dish. The sauce recipe makes about 1 1/2 cups so you could halve it if you don't want leftovers.